def calculate_earnings(n, m, seats):
    max_seats = seats[:]
    min_seats = seats[:]
    max_earnings = 1
    min_earnings = 0
    for _ in range(n):
        x = max(max_seats)
        max_earnings += x
        max_seats[max_seats.index(x)] -= 1
    for _ in range(n):
        x = min(min_seats)
        if x == 0:
            min_seats.remove(x)
        x = min(min_seats)
        min_earnings += x
        min_seats[min_seats.index(x)] -= 1
    return (max_earnings, min_earnings)
